{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"38f9e32a-971e-4fce-9c53-79e64c655b2d","content":"There's no existing workflow file in this directory. Since this is a general guidance question, here's what you need to change:\n\n### Switching to NuGet Trusted Publishing (OIDC)\n\n**1. NuGet.org setup** — Register your GitHub repo as a trusted publisher on [nuget.org/manage](https://www.nuget.org/manage):\n- Go to your package → **Manage** → **Trusted publishers**\n- Add your GitHub repo, branch/tag pattern, and workflow file name\n\n**2. Workflow changes:**\n\n```yaml\n# BEFORE\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      - uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4\n      - run: dotnet pack -c Release\n      - run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg -s https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json -k ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }}\n\n# AFTER\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write  # ← Required for OIDC token\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      - uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4\n      - run: dotnet pack -c Release\n      - run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg -s https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n### Key changes:\n| What | Details |\n|------|---------|\n| **Add** `permissions.id-token: write` | Lets the runner request an OIDC token |\n| **Remove** `-k ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }}` | No API key needed; NuGet authenticates via the OIDC token automatically |\n| **Remove** the `NUGET_API_KEY` secret | Clean up the repo secret once verified |\n\nThe `dotnet nuget push` command (with .NET SDK 9+) automatically detects the GitHub OIDC environment and authenticates without a key. If you're on an older SDK, you may need to explicitly pass `--api-key az` and configure the NuGet service index for token exchange.\n\nWould you like me to create a workflow file for your repo?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"1b02c4f7-9363-4316-9144-0d889e91baa0","outputTokens":544},"id":"eccc66d7-3906-4094-89bf-e3742eca9438","timestamp":"2026-04-08T00:47:11.602Z","parentId":"75dd2773-d3f3-425f-92c0-4c61dc1c9c2c"}
